OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly dry start in the east
OL,6,Fwith some brightness. Cloud and
OL,7,Foccasionally heavy rain in west will
OL,8,Fsoon spread east to all parts, though
OL,9,Fstaying drier in the east. Brighter
OL,10,Fspells developing from the west
OL,11,Fthrough late afternoon. Breezy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny remaining cloud and rain
OL,14,Fsoon clearing east. Otherwise largely
OL,15,Fdry with clear spells through the
OL,16,Fnight, but the odd shower feeding in
OL,17,Ffrom the west. Occasionally blustery
OL,18,Fsouthwest winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
