OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA largely dry morning with
OL,6,Fbright or sunny spells, though with
OL,7,Fthe chance of the odd shower. Cloudier
OL,8,Flater with outbreaks of rain. A bit
OL,9,Fcooler than recent days.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,12,FSaturday morning with outbreaks of
OL,13,Frain, drier and brighter later. Cloudy
OL,14,Fand windy at times Sunday and Monday
OL,15,Fwith occasional spells of rain,
OL,16,Fstaying drier in east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
